'''瑞貝卡·"貝克斯"·愛迪生·泰勒-克勞斯'''（{{lang-en|Rebecca "Bex" Edison Taylor-Klaus}}，{{bd|1994年|8月12日|||catIdx=L}}）是一名出生於[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]][[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]的[[美國|美國]]演員。<ref name="issue">{{cite website |title=BEX TAYLOR-KLAUS |url=https://issuemagazine.com/bex-taylor-klaus/#/ |work=ISSUE Magazine |quote=BIRTH DATE: Aug 12 BIRTH PLACE: Atlanta |access-date={{dts|2019|10|9}} |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203101313/https://issuemagazine.com/bex-taylor-klaus/#/ |archive-date=2020-02-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="ArtsATL">{{cite web |last1=Moore |first1=Christine |date={{dts|2013|7|26}} |title=30 Under 30: Bex Taylor-Klaus bites the bullet and lands dream role on AMC's ''The Killing'' |url=https://www.artsatl.org/30-30-bex-taylor-klaus-bites-bullet-lands-dream-role-amcs-the-killing/ |website=ArtsATL |access-date={{dts|2015|1|15}} |language=en |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010053842/https://www.artsatl.org/30-30-bex-taylor-klaus-bites-bullet-lands-dream-role-amcs-the-killing/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他最知名的作品是[[AMC|AMC]]出品的《{{link-en|謀殺 (美國劇集)|The Killing (American TV series)|謀殺}}》、[[DC娛樂|DC娛樂]]出品的《[[綠箭俠_(電視劇)|綠箭俠]]》以及[[MTV|MTV]]所出品的《[[驚聲尖叫_(電視劇)|驚聲尖叫]]》，在劇中飾演主要角色奧黛莉·詹森。<ref>{{cite journal |first=Whitney |last=Friedlander |url=https://variety.com/2014/tv/news/mtv-orders-scream-tv-show-1201341402/ |title=MTV Orders 'Scream' TV Show to Series |magazine=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date={{dts|2014|10|28}} |access-date={{dts|2015|7|24}} |language=en |journal= |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010053841/https://variety.com/2014/tv/news/mtv-orders-scream-tv-show-1201341402/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Lesley |last=Goldberg |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/mtvs-scream-adaptation-sets-cast-723337 |title=MTV's 'Scream' Adaptation Sets Cast, Director |newspaper=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date={{dts|2014|8|5}} |access-date={{dts|2015|07|2